content.html:
The latest DTS Demo Disc from the CES Show in Vegas 2020. This is Volume 24 from the series. Contains the latest Movie Clips on 4k UHD HDR and DTS:X, DTS-HD MA 7.1 and DTS Headphone:X audio. Also include test tools DTS Callout 7.14 and 5.1.4. Content: Apollo 13 Wolf Warrior 2 SYML Clean Eyes The Scorpion King Recycled Sound Hellboy II: The Golden Army SYML Wildfire Backdraft SHDADOW A Different Perspective Hot Fuzz Westworld Hulk SYML WDWGILY Along With The Gods: The Last 49 Days Old Sea Brigade Hope Tests: DTS Callout 7.1.4 DTS Callout 5.1.4

Watched on Trakt
